content.title: Delayed response times for fallback mechanisms
content.description: Fallback mechanisms in face recognition exhibit delays during high-traffic scenarios. Optimize logic and resource allocation.

content.title: Increased latency for real-time deepfake detection
content.description: Latency spikes occur during peak processing in real-time deepfake detection. Profile and optimize inference pipeline.

content.title: Anomaly detection crashes with large datasets
content.description: The anomaly detection module crashes during batch processing of large datasets. Debug memory usage and optimize resource allocation.

content.title: Misaligned bounding boxes for thermal regions
content.description: Bounding boxes are misaligned during thermal imaging in high-density environments. Review calibration and dataset augmentation.

content.title: Pedestrian detection failures at curved crosswalks
content.description: Model struggles to identify pedestrians at crosswalks with significant curves. Investigate curvature augmentation in training datasets.

content.title: VIP gate processing delays under high load
content.description: Face recognition at VIP gates exhibits delays during simultaneous processing of multiple passengers. Optimize threading logic.

content.title: Model accuracy drops for synthesized audio-video pairs
content.description: Deepfake detection shows reduced accuracy for synthesized audio-video combinations. Augment dataset and retrain models.

content.title: Thermal zone overlap errors during low-light tests
content.description: Errors occur in safety analysis when thermal zones overlap under low-light conditions. Optimize preprocessing for boundary detection.

content.title: Edge case latency for nighttime suburban scenarios
content.description: Latency spikes observed in suburban tests during nighttime pedestrian detection. Profile bottlenecks and refine the pipeline.

content.title: Misclassification during adversarial input testing
content.description: Adversarial inputs with minor pixel alterations cause the deepfake detection model to misclassify. Reinforce training against adversarial examples.

content.title: Anomaly overlay misalignment in QA demos
content.description: During QA demonstrations, anomaly overlays misalign with bounding boxes when thermal layers are active. Debug overlay logic.
